room_title: Escape room "Secret Warehouse" by Zoya Escape Rooms in St. Joseph (MI)
room_address: 4298 S Niles Rd, St Joseph, MI 49085
room_description: Dangerous Stuff is a secret government organization charged with protecting the world from a bizarre range of artifacts that in the wrong hands could cause disaster. The staff at the warehouse was lost in an unfortunate accident, and you and your team have been sent in to replace them, and secure the room in an hour before the artifacts cause any more damage.
